<section id="slr_data">
    <title>slr_data</title>
    <para>This object act as a container for data needed by the specified profile to check the part
    of the JLIFF document that is a sibling or descendant of a sibling of this object. It is not
    used by the default profiles.</para>
    <para><emphasis>Type:</emphasis>
    <?oxy_custom_start type="oxy_content_highlight" color="255,255,0"?>object<?oxy_custom_end?>.</para>
    <simplelist>
    <?oxy_custom_start type="oxy_content_highlight" color="255,64,0"?>
    <member>- elements from other namespaces,
      <glossterm>optional</glossterm><?oxy_custom_end?></member>
  </simplelist>

    <para><emphasis>Properties:</emphasis></para>
    <simplelist>
    <member>- <code>"slr_profile"</code>, a <olink
        targetdoc="../../attributes/size_restriction/profile.xml" targetptr="slr_profile"
          ><code>profile</code></olink> object, <glossterm>required</glossterm></member>
    <?oxy_custom_start type="oxy_content_highlight" color="255,64,0"?>
    <member>- attributes from other namespaces,
      <glossterm>optional</glossterm><?oxy_custom_end?></member>
  </simplelist>

<itemizedlist>
  
  <title>Processing Requirements</title>
    <listitem>
      <para>Third party profiles <glossterm>must</glossterm> place all data in this
        <?oxy_custom_start type="oxy_content_highlight" color="255,255,0"?>object<?oxy_custom_end?>
        instead of using other extension points if the data serves no other purpose in the
        processing of the document.</para>
    </listitem>
    <listitem>
      <para>Data not used by the specified profile <glossterm>must not</glossterm> be placed in this
        <?oxy_custom_start type="oxy_content_highlight" color="255,255,0"?>object<?oxy_custom_end?>.</para>
    </listitem>
  </itemizedlist>

</section>
